doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    title Fitness+ Add-On Service Reminder
  body
    h1 Dear #{name},

    p This is a friendly reminder that your #{description} is due soon.

    p
      strong Amount Due:
      | $#{amount}
    
    p
      strong Due Date:
      | #{dueDate}

    p We appreciate your prompt attention to this matter. If you have already made the payment, please disregard this notice.

    p If you have any questions or need assistance, please do not hesitate to contact our support team.

    p
      | You can download the full invoice here:
      a(href=`https://yourdomain.com/invoices/${invoiceUID}`) #{invoiceUID}

    p Thank you for being a valued member of Fitness+!

    p
      | Best regards,
      br
      | The Fitness+ Team
